nodes.text: A dock warehouse in the capital of Sundari on the planet Mandalore was the site of a shootout between New Mandalorian police and Mandalorian Royal Guard led by Duchess Satine Kryze and Senator Padmé Amidala and Moogan and Gotal smugglers led by Tee Va.
After the shootout, the police burned the warehouse and the smuggled contents within with flamethrowers.
